reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I ordered three sets in three different colors to go with each child’s tablet. They matched perfect, they fit each child’s head, did not slide back-and-forth. Kids were able to tune out outside noise while wearing them.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars True to its description
reviews.reviewText: I bought a pair of these headphones for my eldest child who recently got into listening to music and they're great. They look cute, fit her head well, and truly have a safe volume level (I tested them myself; cranked my volume up all the way and my ear drums were not blown out while wearing them ^•^). The music quality is good for the price I paid~ I got these majorly on sale. No complaints on day one of using these.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Comfortable and durable
reviews.reviewText: My son likes them and the cable is durable. He says they sound good and they let him watch his shows while we are watching ours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Durable kid headphones
reviews.reviewText: This is our second pair and my kids really like these headphones. They said they are really comfortable to wear and the sound is good in them. We had one pair that lasted 3 years with 3 kids sharing them. This pair has the same durability so far. They are really well made and worth the price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Our go to headphones for years
reviews.reviewText: We have a kiddo who has sensory processing disorder & finding headphones that she liked was a journey, nay a quest that started in elementary; kiddo will be a senior this year. We bought A LOT of different headphones at different price points & for one reason or another, she couldn't use them. She tried, she really did but we struck out over & over; too tight, too loose, too pinchy, too squishy, too hard, smelled funny etc, until we found these. We now keep a supply at all times in case they ever stop making them. (please, please don't do that!) Her friends, our niece & nephews, coworkers, art group members all ended up with all the others we didn't use, so bonus for them! She's not rambunctious with them & barring the occasional whoops (dog jumped on sofa, landed on them. I accidentally sat on a set that were also left on the sofa etc.) she wears them everyday almost all day and they can last a couple of years or more (unless she forgets to not leave them on the sofa!!) Sounds fine, mic works for video chat, online class, gaming etc. Comfortable on her ears, cords last the entire time. Breakage does happen after awhile, usually at the hinge. They might not please everyone but we love them! (Request that a black & neon green color scheme be made though! 😉)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Great company to work with.
reviews.reviewText: Look great, work great, but more fragile than I wish considering my kids use them daily and are really hard on stuff. I've bought many pairs, and always end up replacing them about a year later, but I keep buying more of these because they work so great. The company is really awesome to work with too. They replaced a pair free for me, and really went out of their way.I totally recommend these.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Definitely didn’t want to spend a lot on headphones that would be brought to school & back daily. These were affordable, feel solid, nice color. My child just used them for the first time at school & she said they were very comfy & sounded clear so no complaints.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Bought for Christmas gift for grandson - perfect.

reviews.reviewTitle: Muy buena opción para niños y adolescentes
reviews.reviewText: Esta opción de audífonos se me hizo muy buena para mis hijos, las razones:Son resistentes, tienen cierta flexibilidad, lo cual los hace menos propensos a dañarse porque los jalen o doblen.Su cable protegido hace que no tan fácilmente se pueda romper o deteriorar.Todas las superficies en contacto con la cabeza o las orejas están acolchó a dos, lo que los hace cómodos.Los colores son muy llamativos para niños y adolescentes.Tienen un límite en la intensidad de sonido, lo cual se me hace genial para cuidar los oídos de nuestros hijos.Estoy súper contento con esta compra, se los recomiendo.
